<p>Update my band profile </p><button><a href="/user/profile/edit-band">Update
    band</a></button>
<p>Update my band profile picture </p><button><a href="/user/profile/edit-band-avatar">Update
    avatar</a></button>
<p>Delete my band profile </p><button><a href="/user/profile/delete-band">Delete
